Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻过这座山之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 港口之都 哈里 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从 哈里 可以搭船到相邻的 拉克尔 大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克尔 那里有大型的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以找到能解读这本古文书的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有些什么重要的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是在怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟 你是剑士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也进去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才啊 有一位旅行的剑士为了消灭邪恶的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到洞窟里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶的魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都出现在牧场 还把动物吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我养的牲畜全被吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他是剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个人进去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们也进去帮他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 真是些强人所难的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办哪 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有困难的人我们也不能不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是好心人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊… 看你们的啰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什么样的魔物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是能吃掉牛羊的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是非常巨大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险 快出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把村子里的牧场一一捣毁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把他们辛苦养大的家畜吃掉的邪恶魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 艾修顿•安卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替天行道 制裁你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种魔物我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾、蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～两位还真亲热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 龙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是怕了本艾修顿大爷 逃之夭夭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你们那是什么眼神啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你背上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会粘在我的背上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帮我拿下来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～谁来救我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你们害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛把责任都推到我们头上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我全力保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果无法集中精神战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没有保护到谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎完全融合在一起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用蕾娜的治愈能力恢复不了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况的话就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴的纹章术能不能帮帮他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没听说过有那样的纹章术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候玩捉迷藏每次都是我扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足的当天一定会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一走在路上就会踩到屎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我总是背负这种厄运呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜它所赐总是碰到灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果都没人肯陪我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～那么你是孤单一个人出来旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说孤单一个人～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢一个人旅行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来就有新同伴了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的同伴哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以变成这样都是你们害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要负起责任吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办法倒是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前看到过一本书上面是这么记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龙附身者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以飞舞在天空的王者之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来净化其身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞舞在天空的王者之泪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有王者之泪者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宁静的水面所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如母亲体内一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其降临的险峻山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受荣耀的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得胜利之时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝方可得到王者之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时咏诵誓词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着强烈且痛苦的咆哮声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔龙将从世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到飞舞在天空的王者之泪就行了 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宁静的水面所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如母亲体内一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是位于克洛斯大陆西北方的\N克尔湖的山岳神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快点往那个神殿出发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～龙龙它们在吃蛋糕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 可不可以给它们取名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别管这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只眼睛瞪得长长的就叫"长长"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只眼睛圆溜溜的就叫"圆圆"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们很喜欢耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙袭击牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家畜都吃光了耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真的有袭击牧场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都说不是了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别上当！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙这种动物是很凶恶的魔物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们等等我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一觉得自己实在累得要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这两个家伙还真重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只靠我一个人背着你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也给我下来走走行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的废物…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 精神不是超好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刚才那个咖啡店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也给我一块
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长和圆圆也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 你们俩要去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停、停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦 很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我非找到王者之泪不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要特地跑来找魔物打架吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我跟魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么巨大的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按理说会有相当的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要循着波动寻找的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以找到他的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南南西的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感应到强大的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安无事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山脚下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长 圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…想不到我会变成这幅德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太悲哀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…是不是丢下我继续旅行了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得被这种魔物附身不可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用那种邪恶的称呼叫我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？谁…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们在说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我听错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在这种地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 波动非常强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…我们已经离他们很近啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长 圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物的巢穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德 你看那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 袭击牧场的原来是这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～虫子～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 讨厌啦 讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我到前面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再走下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪哪 闪哪 闪哪 闪哪 闪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿 小心上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群玷污魔族崇高名誉的低贱之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是低级的魔物 竟然赶来惹我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是长长和圆圆它们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占据了艾修顿的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加诸于吾等魔族的的恶名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是你们这些魔物\N所干出的下流之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种罪行就用你们的死来洗刷吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空•破•斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚伦那时候一样的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦～虫子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能洗脱嫌疑真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 村里的牧场就不会受到袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能走啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上之所以背着这两坨东东
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把它们弄掉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直跟着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下耳根子又没的清静了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出发咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 克尔湖的山岳神殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克劳德•C•肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在克尔湖的山岳神殿里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们碰到了一位正在寻找恋人的\N不可思议的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶？和我一样\N是来自其它星球的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这时真的话\N这个星球的某个地方应该有宇宙船
